{"tid":2269250,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"健康碼 變身”安心出行”App 月中推出","createTime":"2020-11-03T11:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T11:13:22.000Z","uid":257736,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d542b82743f889351dbc1ced748d08bc48c60ec9","tid":2269250,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明話比市民自己記錄出行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n但又話<span class=\"red\">有助衛生防護中心更有效追蹤新冠病毒確診者的接觸者</span><br />\n<br />\n張建宗又稱，政府正準備推出命名「安心出行」的感染風險通知流動應用程式（App），供市民免費下載，方便市民養成記錄出行的習慣，亦有助衛生防護中心更有效追蹤新冠病毒確診者的接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，「安心出行」流動應用程式由政府資訊科技總監辦公室統籌開發，是自願參與、自主作記錄，出行紀錄只會加密存放於用戶的個人流動電話內，不會備存到任何政府或其他系統。資科辦正與不同部門合作，積極向包括餐飲、卡拉OK、健身中心及的士等業界介紹應用程式，鼓勵更多界別參與。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201101/s00001/1604200082009/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8Dapp%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201101%2Fs00001%2F1604200082009%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258E%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258Dapp%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6a8ca674\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201101%2Fs00001%2F1604200082009%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258E%25A8%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E3%2580%258Dapp%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C&h=1f093ff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201101/s00001/1604200082009/%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A8%E3%80%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%BF%83%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8Dapp%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C</a>"},{"pid":"72e1954a8fce033c9e5388525d3a40a41defc37a","tid":2269250,"uid":53601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frCDx6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfrCDx6U.jpg&h=7f163773&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f83b27a152b1c553d502e4fada13e77184b273a1","tid":2269250,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"安心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}